Power Snatch + Hang Squat Snatch + Overhead Squat (1+1+1)

6 Thrusters (#50/35)
6 Toes-to-bar
6 Box Jumps

Skills:

Rope Climb

Beach WOD (מציצים):
In Pairs:

200m run
(partner 1 - partner 2 does plank hold)
10 synchronized burpees
20 synchronized KB swings
30 synchronized goblet squats
10 m sprint to the water (partner 2)

Rx: 12 / 8 kg


partners can switch the rounds as needed
